(21, 21, 'Crypto Cyber Security', 'Protect your digital assets with industry-leading blockchain and crypto security solutions.', '<p>Crypto cyber security services are designed to protect users and organizations from digital threats targeting blockchain assets. We conduct smart contract audits, secure wallets, and provide infrastructure to defend against phishing, exploits, and unauthorized access. With rising DeFi activity and wallet hacks, strong cyber defense is critical. From hardware wallet setup and multisig access to 24/7 monitoring and response systems, our service ensures peace of mind in a decentralized world where asset protection is non-negotiable.</p>', '<p>Crypto cybersecurity ensures the integrity of assets, data, and smart contracts. It helps users mitigate risks, prevent costly breaches, and maintain compliance in an increasingly complex crypto landscape—protecting both individual users and institutional stakeholders from evolving threats.</p>', '[{\"name\":\"Auditing DeFi smart contracts before launch or listing\"},{\"name\":\"Securing user wallets and exchange platforms from cyber threats\"},{\"name\":\"Setting up cold storage or multisig access for institutional funds\"}]', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-17 12:54:34', '2025-07-26 16:37:54', 'Smart Contract Audits', 'Detect and eliminate vulnerabilities in blockchain code and protocols.', '75', 'Wallet & Exchange Security', 'Protect assets with cold storage, multisig, and biometric security.', '75', '24/7 Threat Monitoring', 'Real-time alerts for suspicious blockchain activity and attack prevention.', '75', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(22, 22, 'Crypto Trading', 'Buy, sell, and swap cryptocurrencies with real-time insights and secure execution.', '<p>Crypto trading services provide users with access to global cryptocurrency markets, enabling the buying, selling, and exchanging of digital assets such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, and altcoins. These platforms offer tools like market charts, order books, limit/market orders, and automated trading bots for optimal strategy execution. Whether you\'re a beginner or a seasoned trader, our platform ensures high liquidity, tight spreads, and responsive interfaces. Traders can also benefit from 24/7 market access, price alerts, and risk management features to make informed decisions in the fast-paced crypto environment.</p>', '<p data-start=\"1565\" data-end=\"1904\">Stay ahead of volatile markets with responsive tools, precision analytics, and instant execution. Whether you\'re a novice or a pro, enjoy access to deep liquidity, secure platforms, and trading flexibility. Reduce risk, maximize gains, and make informed decisions with 24/7 trading support and customizable strategies.</p>', '[{\"name\":\"Day trading or scalping high-volatility crypto markets\"},{\"name\":\"Executing swing trades on major coins and altcoins\"},{\"name\":\"Converting assets between coins during portfolio rebalancing\"}]', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:28:01', '2025-07-26 16:36:48', 'Real-Time Market Data', 'Live price feeds and trading indicators across multiple crypto assets.', '75', 'Advanced Trading Tools', 'Execute strategies using limit orders, stop-loss, and trading bots.', NULL, 'Scalable & Secure', 'Solutions built for growth with strong security and future-ready architecture.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(23, 23, 'Crypto Investment', 'Grow your wealth through diversified, long-term crypto investment strategies and asset management.', '<p>Crypto investment services offer structured opportunities to grow digital wealth via professionally managed portfolios, staking, and DeFi products. These services focus on long-term returns while balancing risk with diversification. Whether through stablecoins, blue-chip tokens, or emerging blockchain projects, your portfolio is optimized using market analysis and predictive algorithms. Get exposure to passive income options like staking and yield farming while ensuring compliance, security, and performance tracking. Ideal for individuals and institutions looking to build sustainable returns in a volatile market.</p>', '<p>Crypto investments provide scalable growth potential, hedge against inflation, and early access to revolutionary technologies. They offer passive income through staking and long-term appreciation of tokens, making them a powerful tool for wealth accumulation in a decentralized financial future.</p>', '[{\"name\":\"Building a long-term crypto investment portfolio\"},{\"name\":\"Earning interest on idle assets via DeFi lending or staking\"},{\"name\":\"Gaining exposure to early-stage blockchain projects\"}]', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:41:32', '2025-07-26 16:37:41', 'Expert-Managed Portfolios', 'Curated crypto baskets tailored to your risk profile and goals.', NULL, 'Passive Income Opportunities', 'Earn through staking, lending, and yield-generating DeFi assets.', NULL, 'Risk Diversification', 'Balanced investments across tokens, sectors, and strategies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(24, 24, 'Crypto Wallet Development', 'Scalable, flexible, and efficient cloud solutions—tailored to your needs for seamless migration, management, and growth.', '<p data-start=\"4278\" data-end=\"4856\">We build secure, user-friendly crypto wallets to store, send, and manage digital currencies. Whether mobile, web-based, or hardware-compatible, our wallets support multi-chain operations, token swaps, and NFT management. Security features include seed phrase encryption, biometric access, and multisig protection. We also integrate support for DeFi apps, DApp browsers, and staking tools. Designed for both individuals and enterprises, our solutions ensure complete control over your assets with robust backend infrastructure and a smooth user interface.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"4858\" data-end=\"4871\"></p>', '<p>Custom wallet development enables direct asset control, user privacy, and secure transaction handling. It provides a branded user experience while ensuring private key safety and integration with DApps, exchanges, and Web3 platforms.</p>', '[{\"name\":\"Launching a branded wallet app for a blockchain startup\"},{\"name\":\"Offering a secure wallet for token and NFT holders\"},{\"name\":\"Enabling wallet users to access DeFi and staking protocols\"}]', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:46:00', '2025-07-26 16:38:09', 'Multi-Chain Support', 'Store and manage tokens across Ethereum, BNB Chain, and more.', NULL, 'DeFi & DApp Integration', 'Seamless access to staking, swaps, and decentralized apps.', NULL, 'Enterprise-Grade Security', 'Biometric login, 2FA, and encrypted private key storage.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(25, 25, 'Crypto Payment Gateway', 'Enable seamless crypto payments on your platform or website for global users.', '<p>A crypto payment gateway allows businesses to accept digital currencies like Bitcoin and USDT for goods and services. Our gateway solutions feature instant conversions, low transaction fees, and integration across websites and e-commerce platforms. Designed for global scalability, our API and plugin solutions let merchants tap into the expanding crypto consumer base while bypassing traditional banking delays.</p>', '<p>Crypto gateways offer real-time, borderless payment acceptance, reducing operational costs and eliminating chargeback risks. They improve customer experience, support new markets, and boost financial inclusion by removing fiat-only barriers.</p>', '[{\"name\":\"Accepting crypto in e-commerce stores\"},{\"name\":\"Global payment solutions for SaaS products\"},{\"name\":\"Enabling crypto donations for NGOs\"}]', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:49:07', '2025-07-26 16:44:54', 'Multi-Coin Payment Support', 'Accept Bitcoin, Ethereum, and stablecoins instantly.', NULL, 'Fiat Conversion Options', 'Auto-convert crypto to fiat to manage volatility.', NULL, 'Easy Checkout Integration', 'Quick plug-ins for Shopify, WooCommerce, and more', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(26, 26, 'Crypto Exchange Development', 'Launch your own cryptocurrency exchange platform with top-tier features and security.', '<p>Crypto exchange development involves creating digital marketplaces for users to buy, sell, or swap cryptocurrencies. We offer turnkey solutions including spot, margin, and peer-to-peer trading modules. Our white-label exchanges come with user-friendly interfaces, KYC/AML systems, liquidity integrations, and bank-grade security. From centralized to decentralized models, we ensure a scalable infrastructure tailored to your business goals.</p>', '<p>Exchange development empowers businesses to tap into the fast-growing crypto economy, generate revenue through trading fees, and create ecosystems that support token projects and financial products—all while maintaining operational transparency and user trust.</p>', '[{\"name\":\"Launching regional crypto trading platforms\"},{\"name\":\"Enabling token listing for ICOs\"},{\"name\":\"Building P2P exchanges for emerging markets\"}]', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:50:45', '2025-07-26 16:48:05', 'White-Label Architecture', 'Fully customizable exchange with fast deployment.', NULL, 'Liquidity Aggregation', 'Ensure deep order books for smooth trades.', NULL, 'Compliance Modules', 'Integrated KYC, AML, and tax reporting tools.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

